                            <comment id="13007074" author="yuzhihong@gmail.com" created="Tue, 15 Mar 2011 18:31:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Also includes the change of HServerLoad.regionLoad to Map.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
